For example, you can call the `list_steps` for the running steps only.
```
response = client.list_steps(
    ClusterId=&#39;string&#39;,
    StepStates=[&#39;RUNNING&#39;]
)
```
Then it will give you below response.
```
{
    &#39;Steps&#39;: [
        {
